{
  "id": "lq9GQV1S",
  "slug": "witcher_medalions",
  "title": "Witcher Medalions",
  "description": "A mod that adds witcher medallions. Now you can pass the medallion trial to create your own medallion and hit the trail!",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/3102f6aa7a3cec69412f0137114f6ce7f151dc8a.png\" width=\"1103\" height=\"86\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/7ebb3e267ba69f91dcc169cf61150be578207bf5.png\" width=\"1645\" height=\"301\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong>\"Cisza! Słuchać mnie teraz adepci!</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong>Oto przed wami ostateczny test. Ostateczna pr&oacute;ba. Pr&oacute;ba medalionu!</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong>Ten, kto cały z medalionem wr&oacute;ci, dowiedzie, że jest go godzien i na szlak wstąpić może&rdquo;&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;\"><strong>\"Witcher Medalions\" to modyfikacja kt&oacute;ra wprowadza do gry medaliony związane z każdą szkołą wiedźmińską z uniwersum Wiedźmina. Gracz ma możliwość stworzenia medalion&oacute;w za pomocą rytualnego kamienia, na kt&oacute;rym wiedźmini zakończają swoje pr&oacute;by medalionu.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/b614efc9dd4f9435c65e7e53c8ab68f6b1eae54f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong>(Rytualny kamień)</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong>Aby stworzyć rytualny kamień, potrzebne są następujące składniki: 3 bloki bruku, 4 pochodnie, miseczka z wodą (miska + butelka/wiadro z wodą) oraz blok ziemi oraz st&oacute;ł rzemieślniczy na kt&oacute;rym należy owe bloki ułożyć zgodnie z instrukcją przedstawioną na załączonym obrazku:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/cfbd4c473afdf4ab51cdaec3dcad88b2fc8339b8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"555\" height=\"280\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/c71fb769e418a718dc2f3c2725551876913cc77c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"557\" height=\"281\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong>Aby stworzyć medalion potrzebna jest&nbsp;bryłka srebra:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/c9a5e6384d082956d24f958ba6d3211969e9bced.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"132\" height=\"145\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong>Ten cenny surowiec można wytopić z rudy srebra, kt&oacute;rą można odnaleźć razem z innymi minerałami kopiąc w kopalni. Gdy srebro zostanie wytopione należy udać się z nim do kamienia rytualnego by nasycić medalion energią czterech żywioł&oacute;w. Po rytuale jako pełnoprawny wiedźmin możesz już przemierzać szlak!</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/6b2fdaeb8cc726fe2643817bd00d361cc711e92b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"953\" height=\"99\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong>Jeśli masz medalion w ekwipunku możesz wykrywać pobliskie potwory za pomocą klawisza \"R\"</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; color: #000000;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/0912f86bc0c64f6a3afd5d79be0b55056c29d20b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1126\" height=\"564\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px; color: #000000; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif;\">Translated:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif;\"><strong>\"Silence! Hear me now adepts!</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif;\"><strong>Here is the final test before you. The ultimate trial. Medallion Trial!</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif;\"><strong>Whoever returns with the medallion will prove that he is worthy and can join the trail.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>\"Witcher Medallions\" is a modification that adds medallions to the game related to each witcher school from the Witcher universe. The player has the option to create medallions using a ritual stone on which witchers end their medallion trials.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/b614efc9dd4f9435c65e7e53c8ab68f6b1eae54f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>(Ritual Stone)</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>To create a ritual stone, you need the following ingredients: 3 cobblestone blocks, 4 torches, a bowl of water (bowl + water bottle/bucket) and a block of earth and a crafting table on which to place these blocks according to the instructions presented in the attached picture:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/cfbd4c473afdf4ab51cdaec3dcad88b2fc8339b8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"555\" height=\"280\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/c71fb769e418a718dc2f3c2725551876913cc77c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"557\" height=\"281\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>To create a medallion, you need a silver nugget:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/c9a5e6384d082956d24f958ba6d3211969e9bced.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"132\" height=\"145\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>This precious resource can be smelted from silver ore, which can be found along with other minerals by digging in the mine. When the silver is smelted, go with it to the ritual stone to imbue the medallion with the energy of the four elements. After the ritual, as a full-fledged witcher, you can now travel the trail!</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/6b2fdaeb8cc726fe2643817bd00d361cc711e92b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"953\" height=\"99\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>If you have a medallion in your inventory, you can detect nearby monsters with the \"R\" key</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'book antiqua', palatino, serif; font-size: 24px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lq9GQV1S/images/0912f86bc0c64f6a3afd5d79be0b55056c29d20b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1126\" height=\"564\" /></strong></span></p>",
